Precis1. DEPARTMENT OF AGRICULTURE TERMS UNDER SIX MONTHS EXCLUSION APPROVAL ORDER, 1990; and 2. DEPARTMENT OF AGRICULTURE TERMS UNDER SIX MONTHS REGULATIONS, 1990 - which exempt the employment of certain persons who work in the Technical, Operational or Administrative Support Categories for one or more periods of less than six months in the aggregate from the application of certain provisions of the Public Service Employment Act.
